---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contacto
permalink: /contacto/
---

<section class="px-8 py-20 sm:px-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-terracotta-50 to-white">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-warm-gray-800 mb-4">Contacto</h1>
    <span class="block w-16 h-1 bg-terracotta-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-10"></span>
    <p class="text-lg text-warm-gray-700 mb-10">
      ¿Quieres escribirnos, proponer un proyecto o saber más sobre nuestros libros? Estos son nuestros canales.
    </p>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="block bg-white border border-terracotta-200 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-terracotta-300 transition-all">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-terracotta-600 mb-2">Correo</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-warm-gray-800 font-medium">{{ site.email }}</p>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ site.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-white border border-terracotta-200 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-terracotta-300 transition-all">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-terracotta-600 mb-2">Instagram</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-warm-gray-800 font-medium">{{ site.instagramHandle }}</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
